data.description: Luxury 55+ living, this Mediterranean home boasts a granite kitchen w/ breakfast bar, expansive tile floors, updated master suite and has been painted and refreshed from top to botom. Features include: 2-car garage, screened-in lanai providing a serene space. The main bed and bath offers 2 walk-in closets, a lavish soaking tub and separate shower, while the 2nd bedroom features an adjacent bath.Resort-style amenities include: 4 Pools, tennis and pickleball courts, and walking paths. Clubs cater to diverse interests and camaraderie, while two 24-hour manned gates provide security. Walk to the renovated Clubhouse exuding luxury and entertainment, with indoor/outdoor waitered Bistro dining, arts and crafts studio, and more. Lifestyle Director curates captivating shows and activities
